Harmony Sirens[dnd-info]=Enchanting aquatic beings residing near hidden water sources (often within shells) within jungle areas. These beings can be appear similar to various natural aquatic creatures but come in all shapes and sizes. Their melodic songs can either soothe or agitate nearby creatures, and skilled bards seek them out to learn rare and powerful musical compositions.
